{"root":{"data":{"id":"djin8axefug0","created":1782442775759,"text":"测铜绿微囊藻昼夜 pH 曲线"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djin8unq1ww0","created":1782442818709,"text":"铜绿微囊藻正常培养\n\t           ↓\n12 h 光 / 12 h 暗\n\t           ↓\n用 pH 计每 2–4 h 测一次 bulk pH\n\t           ↓\n连续测 2–3 个昼夜周期\n\t           ↓\n得到真实 pH 曲线","font-family":"times new roman","font-size":16},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djinanq0zxs0","created":1782442960340,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}